ZH: 这本书的答案在最后一页。
EN: The answer to this book is on the last page.

ZH: 我已经找到了这道题的答案。
EN: I have already found the answer to this question.

ZH: 他总是知道所有问题的答案。
EN: He always knows the answer to all the questions.

ZH: 你能告诉我这道数学题的答案吗？
EN: Can you tell me the answer to this math problem?

ZH: 这个问题没有一个明确的答案。
EN: This question does not have a definite answer.

ZH: 我们现在还找不到这个问题的答案。
EN: We still don't have the answer to this question.

ZH: 学生们必须用自己的话来写出答案。
EN: Students have to write the answers in their own words.

ZH: 这位老师从来不直接给学生们答案。
EN: This teacher never gives direct answers to the students.

ZH: 缺乏信息使得找到答案变得更加困难。
EN: The lack of information makes it even harder to find the answer.

ZH: 我们需要同心协力才能找到问题的答案。
EN: We need to work together to find the answer to the problem.

ZH: 这个谜题的答案就在你面前。
EN: The answer to this riddle is right in front of you.

ZH: 我们需要更多的证据来得到一个确切的答案。
EN: We need more evidence to obtain a definite answer.

ZH: 解答这个问题需要一些时间。
EN: It takes some time to solve this problem.

ZH: 请你在纸上写下你的答案。
EN: Please write your answer on the paper.

ZH: 我的姐姐是所有难题的答案。
EN: My sister is the answer to all the difficult questions.

ZH: 这个问题的答案并不复杂。
EN: The answer to this question is not complicated.

ZH: 这个英语考试的答案会在下周公布。
EN: The answers to this English exam will be announced next week.

ZH: 我们需要一个精确的答案来解决争论。
EN: We need an exact answer to resolve the argument.

ZH: 这个问题的答案已经得到了证实。
EN: The answer to this question has been confirmed.

ZH: 请在答案后面写上你的姓名。
EN: Please write your name after the answer.
